CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 21, 2005

[Cite as 03/21/2005 Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-1211.]

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2004-2166. Stark Commons, Ltd. v. Stein Mart, Inc.

Stark App. No. 2004CA00029, 2004-Ohio-6969. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
